3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper considers the maximum regret objective, which is a concept used in machine learning to evaluate the performance of algorithms. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper deals with scheduling under uncertainty, which is a common problem in artificial intelligence.
